726618f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - Union Turnpike
726618f-a.text:
Flushing Meadow Park (Queens): The car yards of New York
City's Independent System Subway at the south end of the park,
viewing eastward from Cueens Boulevnrd and Union Turnpike. Note
road construction for the World's Fsir 1939-40.
View 1 April 23, 1936
View 2: June 29, 1936
View 3: July 7, 1940
P. L. Sperr
